🌌 Vision 2030: The Evolution into "Living Infrastructure"
The IVSCS project transcends traditional automotive safety by reimagining the tire as a conscious, self-sustaining, and diagnostic organ of the vehicle. Below is the technical roadmap for our three core futuristic pillars:

1️⃣ Zero-Power Energy Harvesting ⚡
Concept: Kinetic-to-Electric Conversion

To eliminate the dependency on bulky internal batteries or complex wiring, IVSCS proposes a self-powering ecosystem integrated within the tire's structure.

The Technology: By embedding Piezoelectric Nanogenerators (PENGs) within the tire's inner carcass, we leverage the high-frequency mechanical deformation (stress) and road vibrations generated during rotation.

The Mechanism: Every time the tire contact patch touches the road, the mechanical energy is converted into micro-watts of electrical power through the piezoelectric effect.

The Impact: This creates a perpetual energy loop, ensuring the sensor grid remains active for the entire lifecycle of the tire without ever needing a recharge or external power source.

